name: LEGO Star Wars: The Skywalker Saga - The Mandalorian: Season 1 - Character Pack
summary: This is the Way. Play as the iconic characters from the hit series The Mandalorian Season 1. Travel around the galaxy as The Mandalorian protecting Grogu at all costs. The character pack includes: - The Mandalorian - Cara Dune - Greef Karga - IG-11 - Kuiil
